{"tid":485461,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加成功羅致巴塞人","createTime":"2017-12-01T03:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T10:54:35.000Z","uid":46892,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"b7e9f26b16a204d40efd36d9fd3ebe149fd3eaa5","tid":485461,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:27:51.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=mavyREW5k88UA4jwoGrOxb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=a81ecd60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】這幾年，阿仙奴不少猛將被巴塞隆拿收購，但雲加今次終於打贏一仗，從巴塞購入新援，說的是總監！<br />\n<br />\n英超勁旅阿仙奴日前官方宣佈，擔任巴塞隆拿總監長達14年的辛列希（Raul Sanllehi）正式過檔，將於來年2月履新。官方聲明表示：「辛列希過去14年為巴塞隆拿服務，將在明年2月為阿仙奴負責球員轉會談判，與領隊和行政總裁密切合作。」<br />\n<br />\n兵工廠積極進行內部改革，早前已引入多蒙特首席球探，球會行政總裁加齊迪斯坦言：「過去3年我們已經為幕後團隊進行補充，羅致世界不同領域的頂級人才，辛列希在足壇人脈甚廣，亦是多宗大交易的談判專家。」"},{"pid":"a022bfb894a3758b1b3178c3999ba3a199f5ffd3","tid":485461,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:28:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005ef92a350c6b27c646a3dcd800a139eee5c693","tid":485461,"uid":33601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:33:32.000Z","msg":"雲加又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3c0aec332bf5ae701d6b2e2c6288a20d4f23a0","tid":485461,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:37:34.000Z","msg":"wenger wins<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4647d7386dfea0878e4e2ac5980c594a4c0a3e1f","tid":485461,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:37:54.000Z","msg":"迷雲必勝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c22076e72313d51884df9d21ac5673b0ea6fcf","tid":485461,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-0